(ijs nwm-pdwrQ nUM) dyvqy mnu`K monDwrI lok qrsdy Aw rhy hn auh (pdwrQ) siqgurU ny smJw id`qw hY ]4]
ikho ijhy iek`T nUM sq sMgq smJxw cwhIdw hY?
(sqsMgq auh hY) ij`Qy isr& prmwqmw dw nwm slwihAw jWdw hY[
hy nwnk! siqgurU ny ieh g`l smJw id`qI hY ik (sqsMgq ivc) isr& prmwqmw dw nwm jpxw hI (pRBU dw) hukm hY ]5]
ieh jgq mwieAw dI Btkxw ivc pY ky jIvn dy shI rwh qoN lWBy jw irhw hY[
(pr jIvW dy kIh v`s? hy pRBU!) qUM Awp hI (jgq nUM) Awpxy Awp qoN ivCoiVAw hoieAw hY[
ijn@W mMd-Bwgx jIv-iesqRIAW dy cMgy Bwg nhIN hn, auhnW nUM (mwieAw dy moh ivc Psx dy kwrn Awqmk) du`K l`gw hoieAw hY ]6]
mMd-Bwgx jIv-iesqRIAW dy kI l`Cx hn?
(mMd-Bwgx, jIv-iesqRIAW auh hn) jyhVIAW Ksm-pRBU qoN KuMJIAW hoeIAW hn qy inAwsrIAW ho ky Btk rhIAW hn[
AjyhIAW jIv-iesqRIAW dy cyhry BI ivkwrW dI mYl nwl BirSty hoey id`sdy hn, auhnW dI izMdgI-rUp rwq du`KW ivc hI bIqdI hY ]7]
jyhVIAW jIv-iesqRIAW BwgW vwlIAW AKvWdIAW hn auhnW kyhVw (cMgw kMm) kIqw hoieAw hY?
auhnW ny ipCly jnm ivc kIqI nyk kmweI dy ilKy sMskwrW vjoN hux prmwqmw dw nwm-Pl pRwpq kr ilAw hY[
prmwqmw AwpxI imhr dI ingwh kr ky Awp hI auhnW nUM Awpxy crnW ivc imlw lYNdw hY ]8]
prmwqmw ijn@W jIv-iesqRIAW nUM Awpxw hukm mMnx leI pRyrdw hY,
auh Awpxy ihrdy ivc prmwqmw dI is&q-swlwh dI bwxI vsWdIAW hn[
auhI jIv-shylIAW BwgW vwlIAW huMdIAW hn, ijn@W dw Awpxy Ksm-pRBU nwl ipAwr bixAw rihMdw hY ]9]
ijn@W mnu`KW nUM prmwqmw dI rzw ivc qurn dw AwnMd Aw jWdw hY,
auh Awpxy AMdroN mwieAw vwlI Btkxw dUr kr lYNdy hn (pr ieh imhr siqgurU dI hI hY)[
hy nwnk! gurU Ajyhw (idAwl) hY ik auh (srn Awey) sB jIvW nUM pRBU-crnW ivc imlw dyNdw hY ]10]
aus mnu`K ny gurU dI srn pY ky prmwqmw dw nwm-rs pRwpq kr ilAw,
ijs mnu`K ny Awpxy AMdroN AhMkwr dUr kr ilAw[
aus mnu`K dy AMdroN BYVI m`q dw du`K k`itAw jWdw hY, aus dy m`Qy au~qy Bwg jwg pYNdw hY ]11]
(hy pRBU!) qyrI is&q-swlwh dI bwxI (mwno) Awqmk jIvn dyx vwlw jl hY,
ieh bwxI qyry BgqW dy ihrdy ivc (hr vyly) itkI rihMdI hY[
qyrI suKdweI syvw-BgqI BgqW dy AMdr itkx kr ky qUM auhnW au~qy AwpxI imhr dI ingwh krdw hYN qy auhnW nUM pwr lMGw dyNdw hYN ]12]
qdoN (iksy vfBwgI nUM) gurU imilAw smJxw cwhIdw hY,
jy gurU dy imlx nwl prmwqmw dw nwm ismirAw jwey[
gurU dI srn pYx qoN ibnw (prmwqmw dw nwm) nhIN imldw, (gurU dw Awsrw C`f ky) swrI dunIAw (qIrQ vrq Awidk hor hor imQy hoey Dwrimk) kMm kr ky Kp jWdI hY ]13]
mYN (qW) gurU qoN kurbwn hW,
ijs ny Btkxw ivc kurwhy pey jIv nUM shI jIvn-rwh qy pwieAw hY[
jy gurU AwpxI imhr dI ingwh kry, qW auh Awp hI (pRBU-crnW ivc) joV dyNdw hY ]14]
(hy pRBU!) qUM swry jIvW ivc ivAwpk hYN[
(swry jIvW ivc ivAwpk huMidAW BI) aus krqwr ny Awpxy Awp nUM gupq r`iKAw hoieAw hY[
hy nwnk! ijs mnu`K dy AMdr gurU dI rwhIN krqwr ny AwpxI joiq prgt kIqI hY, aus dy AMdr krqwr prgt ho jWdw hY ]15]
Ksm-pRBU ny (Awpxy syvk nUM) Awp hI vifAweI id`qI hY,
ijMd qy srIr dy ky Awp hI aus nUM pYdw kIqw hY[
Awpxy dovyN h`Q syvk dy isr au~qy r`K ky Ksm-pRBU ny Awp hI aus dI lwj r`KI hY (qy aus nUM ivkwrW qoN bcwieAw hY) ]16]
ieMdRIAW nUM v`s krn dy swry jqn qy ieho ijhIAW hor swrIAW isAwxpW syvk nUM krn dI loV nhIN pYNdI[
ipAwrw pRBU syvk dI hryk loV Awp jwxdw hY[
prmwqmw Awpxy syvk dw qyj-pRqwp prgt kr dyNdw hY, swrw jgq aus dI jY-jYkwr krdw hY ]17]
pRBU ny nwh myry guxW dw ^iAwl kIqw hY, nwh myry AOguxW dI prvwh kIqI hY,
pRBU ny qW isr& Awpxw mu`F-kdImW dw suBwau hI cyqy r`iKAw hY[
aus ny mYnUM Awpxy gl nwl lw ky (ivkwrW vloN) bcw ilAw hY, koeI du`K-ivkwr myrw vwl ivMgw nhIN kr sky ]18]
mYN Awpxy mn ivc pRBU nUM ismirAw hY Awpxy ihrdy ivc pRBU nUM iDAwieAw hY[
mYnUM auh nwm-Pl iml igAw hY, ijs dI mYN sdw Awpxy jI ivc ie`Cw kirAw krdw sW[
hy pRBU! qUM swry SwhW dy isr au~qy, qUM pwiqSwhW dy isr au~qy mwlk hYN[ hy nwnk! (vfBwgI mnu`K) pRBU dw nwm jp ky Awqmk jIvn pRwpq kr lYNdw hY ]19]
